data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION, step inside and be greeted by a spacious 4-bedroom 2.5-bathroom home awaits you. The living room features natural lighting that bathe the space. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living area to the kitchen, making it ideal for entertaining and creating cherished memories. The well-appointed kitchen boasts plenty of cabinet and countertop space, a kitchen island, a pantry for storage, and a modern new refrigerator. Adjacent to the kitchen is a cozy breakfast nook, perfect for enjoying morning coffee or casual meals. Just off the kitchen is the formal dining room. The laundry closet complete with the washer and dryer is on the first floor. All the bedrooms are on the second floor. The Owners bedroom is a serene retreat, complete with its own bathroom for added convenience and privacy, double vanities, soaking tub, and separate shower plus a water closet for privacy. Three additional bedrooms offer ample space. Outside, the backyard offers a private oasis providing an excellent spot for outdoor gatherings or relaxation. The well-maintained lawn adds to the tranquility of the space. Conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping centers, and dining, this home offers easy access to everything Jacksonville has to offer. Commuting is a breeze. Don't miss the chance to make this beauty your new home. Embrace a lifestyle of comfort and convenience in this lovely property.
